00:37.246 --> 00:42.468
<i>The Pilgrim's Progress.
From this World to That Which is to Come,</i>

00:43.335 --> 00:46.214
<i>Delivered Under the Similitude of a Dream.</i>

00:48.632 --> 00:52.387
<i>Wherein is Discovered,
The Manner of His Setting Out,</i>

00:52.928 --> 00:54.680
<i>His Dangerous Journey</i>

00:55.556 --> 00:58.560
<i>And Safe Arrival at the Desired Country.</i>

01:48.817 --> 01:52.412
<i>As I walked through
the wilderness of this world,</i>

01:52.529 --> 01:55.954
<i>I lighted on a certain place
where was a den</i>

01:57.159 --> 01:59.787
<i>and I laid me down in that place to sleep.</i>

02:00.704 --> 02:04.208
<i>And as I slept, I dreamed a dream.</i>

02:06.084 --> 02:09.429
<i>I saw a man clothed with rags,</i>

02:09.588 --> 02:14.389
<i>standing in a certain place with
his face from his own house</i>

02:14.551 --> 02:18.852
<i>book in his hand,
and a great burden upon his back.</i>

02:22.643 --> 02:24.862
<i>All those years...</i>

02:26.938 --> 02:28.940
<i>living the life of someone...</i>

02:30.692 --> 02:32.239
<i>I didn't even know.</i>

03:01.014 --> 03:05.690
<i>Remember the story
I used to tell you when you were a boy...</i>

03:06.520 --> 03:08.113
<i>about a young prince.</i>

03:09.648 --> 03:11.696
<i>A knight,</i>

03:12.567 --> 03:15.286
<i>sent by his father, the King of the East,</i>

03:17.614 --> 03:19.161
<i>west into Egypt...</i>

03:23.578 --> 03:25.125
<i>to find a pearl.</i>

03:30.919 --> 03:34.014
<i>A pearl from the depths of the sea.</i>

03:44.474 --> 03:46.568
<i>But when the prince arrived,</i>

03:49.229 --> 03:53.075
<i>the people poured him a cup
that took away his memory.</i>

03:55.902 --> 03:58.200
<i>He forgot he was the son of the king.</i>

04:04.703 --> 04:06.455
<i>Forgot about the pearl...</i>

04:13.086 --> 04:15.384
<i>and fell into a deep sleep.</i>

04:35.901 --> 04:38.780
<i>The king didn't forget his son.</i>

04:40.947 --> 04:43.370
<i>He continued to send word...</i>

04:47.871 --> 04:49.418
<i>messengers...</i>

04:54.836 --> 04:56.634
<i>guides.</i>

05:00.383 --> 05:03.603
<i>But the prince... slept on.</i>

08:43.565 --> 08:46.034
<i>You see the palm trees?</i>

08:47.027 --> 08:49.405
<i>They tell you anything's possible.</i>

08:53.074 --> 08:54.621
<i>You can be anything...</i>

08:56.703 --> 08:58.250
<i>do anything...</i>

09:00.582 --> 09:02.129
<i>start over.</i>

09:06.004 --> 09:07.551
<i>You know?</i>

09:10.216 --> 09:14.062
I'm asking for your permission to make this

09:14.220 --> 09:17.269
a dramatic scene for one second...

09:41.247 --> 09:42.794
<i>My son...</i>

09:51.049 --> 09:52.596
<i>you are just like I am.</i>

09:58.681 --> 10:00.524
<i>Can't figure your life out?</i>

10:04.896 --> 10:06.990
<i>Can't put the pieces together?</i>

10:13.404 --> 10:15.406
<i>Just like me.</i>

10:23.456 --> 10:25.083
<i>A pilgrim on this earth.</i>

10:29.379 --> 10:30.926
<i>A stranger.</i>

10:54.195 --> 10:55.947
<i>Fragments...</i>

10:59.159 --> 11:00.706
<i>pieces...</i>

11:02.996 --> 11:04.543
<i>of a man.</i>

11:16.426 --> 11:18.724
<i>Where did I go wrong?</i>

11:58.092 --> 12:00.390
<i>What you wanna talk about?</i>

12:03.097 --> 12:05.316
You have nice eyes.

12:05.808 --> 12:07.355
Aren't I lucky.

12:07.936 --> 12:09.654
Where do you live?

12:09.812 --> 12:11.359
Why do ya wanna know?

12:12.649 --> 12:14.492
I want to write you a letter.

12:18.947 --> 12:21.416
What are you gonna say in your letter?

12:26.287 --> 12:28.665
Maybe you better not say it.

13:11.332 --> 13:14.962
<i>Let's live
like nobody's ever done it before.</i>

13:17.547 --> 13:18.594
<i>Wicked.</i>

13:18.756 --> 13:22.010
<i>Once the soul
was perfect and had wings...</i>

13:22.176 --> 13:23.519
<i>Brave.</i>

13:23.678 --> 13:29.060
<i>...it could soar into heaven
where only creatures with wings can be.</i>

13:29.267 --> 13:33.067
<i>But the soul lost its wings
and fell to Earth.</i>

13:33.229 --> 13:35.323
<i>There it took an earthly body.</i>

13:35.523 --> 13:38.367
<i>And now, while it lives in this body,</i>

13:38.526 --> 13:41.700
<i>no outward sign of wings can be seen.</i>

13:42.196 --> 13:44.995
<i>Yet the roots of its wings are still there.</i>

13:45.158 --> 13:48.833
<i>And the nature of wings is to try to raise
the earthbound body</i>

13:48.995 --> 13:50.747
<i>and soar with it into heaven.</i>

13:50.913 --> 13:55.919
<i>When we see a beautiful woman, or a man...</i>

13:56.502 --> 14:01.804
<i>the soul remembers the beauty
it used to know in heaven.</i>

14:02.425 --> 14:07.647
<i>And wings begin to spout,
and that makes the soul want to fly,</i>

14:07.805 --> 14:10.433
<i>but it cannot yet.
It is still too weak.</i>

14:10.600 --> 14:15.481
<i>So the man keeps staring up
into the sky like a young bird.</i>

14:15.646 --> 14:18.195
<i>He has lost
all interest in the world...</i>

14:18.941 --> 14:23.822
<i>- Can I come over?
- We just left each other.</i>

14:23.988 --> 14:25.706
<i>Are you alone?</i>

14:27.450 --> 14:28.997
<i>Of course.</i>

14:29.160 --> 14:34.712
On my phone sheet, I got agent
writers up my ass trying to get this job.

14:34.874 --> 14:39.095
<i>I just want to sit next to you.</i>

14:40.213 --> 14:43.342
Teddy thinks
you're the guy for this.

14:44.675 --> 14:47.770
That means the assignment
you didn't turn in, right,

14:47.929 --> 14:51.274
you don't have to worry about it.
Here's what happens. That goes away.

14:52.266 --> 14:56.271
<i>- What are you wearing?
- A dress.</i>

14:56.437 --> 14:59.190
- <i>What's it made of?
- How should I know?</i>

15:00.400 --> 15:01.947
<i>Cotton, I guess.</i>

15:02.110 --> 15:04.989
We said there's no way
you're gonna do it.

15:05.154 --> 15:08.749
So what'd we do? Said, double your quote.
And he did it.

15:09.242 --> 15:12.917
And that, Chuck signed off of that.
Teddy gets who he wants.

15:13.079 --> 15:15.173
The biggest comedy star wants you.

15:15.331 --> 15:19.757
Five years ago you came to me and
wanted to write big movies in Hollywood.

15:20.837 --> 15:24.216
- I mean...
- Okay, I don't want to see.

15:24.382 --> 15:28.558
Moments like this
don't come along, okay? This is it.

15:37.728 --> 15:39.822
<i>I see how you look at me.</i>

15:45.153 --> 15:47.622
<i>You think I could make you crazy?</i>

15:51.576 --> 15:53.670
<i>Crack you out of your shell?</i>

16:02.420 --> 16:03.967
<i>Make you suffer?</i>

16:26.944 --> 16:33.202
I... think... you're... weak.

16:44.670 --> 16:46.217
<i>You don't want love.</i>

16:52.261 --> 16:54.935
<i>You want a love experience.</i>

17:12.281 --> 17:14.282
Am I bringing you back to life?

17:25.294 --> 17:26.796
<i>Love and do what you like.</i>

17:30.633 --> 17:32.180
<i>A saint said that.</i>

17:38.808 --> 17:40.810
<i>Desire so deep.</i>

17:43.104 --> 17:44.697
<i>I'll throw my life away.</i>

17:47.191 --> 17:49.569
<i>Don't go back to being dead.</i>

18:00.454 --> 18:02.127
<i>What do you want?</i>

18:29.859 --> 18:33.113
We're not leading the lives
that we are meant for.

18:37.241 --> 18:39.744
We're meant for something else.

19:32.254 --> 19:35.224
My brother will translate.

19:52.108 --> 19:54.236
He looks around.

20:01.659 --> 20:04.412
He walks near the edge of the cliff.

20:25.099 --> 20:27.727
She says, like shadows.

20:39.405 --> 20:41.783
<i>Where will I meet you?</i>

20:57.590 --> 20:59.684
<i>Which way should I go?</i>

21:10.853 --> 21:12.855
<i>Suppose it isn't there for me,</i>

21:14.732 --> 21:16.279
<i>in the end?</i>

21:42.092 --> 21:43.639
<i>How do I begin?</i>

22:37.731 --> 22:39.574
<i>Remember how you showed up?</i>

22:40.985 --> 22:44.239
<i>Your wrists were taped up
like a tennis player's.</i>

22:46.490 --> 22:49.539
<i>You walked around
like nothing had happened.</i>

22:54.373 --> 22:58.298
<i>You were always doing it,
pretending everything was okay.</i>

23:00.087 --> 23:01.714
<i>But it wasn't.</i>

23:14.560 --> 23:16.904
- That's my brother, Rick.
- How are ya?

23:17.062 --> 23:20.282
What's goin' on, now? Anything.
Same today?

23:21.191 --> 23:25.367
Don't know how many times
I thought I'd die right here on the street.

23:26.614 --> 23:30.585
I picked him up and I had him
in my car, and a cop pulled us over.

23:30.701 --> 23:36.128
I tell him, "I'm a Methodist minister
and I'm looking after you, alright?"

23:36.290 --> 23:37.837
And I got off.

24:08.238 --> 24:13.460
<i>I dreamed that we were caught in
a huge tidal wave that engulfed the city.</i>

24:16.914 --> 24:20.168
<i>Any moment it seemed like
we might be swept under.</i>

24:23.545 --> 24:26.674
<i>There was a door
that I was afraid to go through.</i>

24:29.218 --> 24:32.973
<i>- I touched the knob...
- If I stuck you with a fork.</i>

24:34.974 --> 24:37.773
<i>Just wanna feel somethin', man.</i>

24:40.396 --> 24:42.319
<i>Wish we could do some things.</i>

24:44.108 --> 24:47.703
<i>Like goin' out on the Snake River together.
Remember?</i>

24:50.406 --> 24:52.579
<i>Think I'd end up here.</i>

24:55.911 --> 24:57.458
<i>Gracias.</i>

25:05.421 --> 25:07.765
It's good of you to invite me out here.

25:09.925 --> 25:12.678
Show me what it's like
to live a normal life.

25:21.395 --> 25:23.318
Somethin' wrong?

25:31.572 --> 25:33.119
What's up?

25:34.158 --> 25:37.412
I can tell when somethin's wrong, man.
I know you.

25:56.055 --> 25:58.683
What do you wanna talk about?

26:03.270 --> 26:06.524
I'm the only brother you got left.
You can tell me.

26:07.399 --> 26:08.946
I tell you stuff.

26:09.818 --> 26:11.912
<i>I loved my brother then.</i>

26:14.698 --> 26:16.245
<i>I hated him, too.</i>

26:18.702 --> 26:21.956
<i>For destroying everything
I'd been trying to do.</i>

26:22.956 --> 26:25.334
<i>To build us back up after Billy died.</i>

26:28.921 --> 26:34.223
I remember when they were putting Billy
in the ground, Dad went into hysterics.

26:35.761 --> 26:37.308
"My son!"

26:38.013 --> 26:39.560
Who fucking does that?

26:41.975 --> 26:44.194
<i>They said he took his life.</i>

26:45.896 --> 26:47.443
<i>But they don't know.</i>

26:51.693 --> 26:53.912
Oh, right now. Come on.

26:56.657 --> 26:58.204
I gotta feel something.

26:58.408 --> 26:59.955
<i>Like a snake.</i>

27:03.914 --> 27:05.461
<i>Swallowed him.</i>

27:06.625 --> 27:08.172
Come on, feel it.

27:16.009 --> 27:17.682
<i>Blind.</i>

27:22.015 --> 27:23.062
<i>Deaf.</i>

27:34.778 --> 27:36.325
<i>Grasping.</i>

27:37.114 --> 27:39.833
<i>I just wanted to twist a cane.</i>

27:43.996 --> 27:45.748
<i>Strike out, break free.</i>

27:47.791 --> 27:49.293
<i>Didn't have the guts.</i>

28:00.053 --> 28:01.976
<i>He's just an old fool.</i>

28:06.435 --> 28:08.813
<i>Just let him die with his blinders on.</i>

28:29.291 --> 28:31.134
<i>Redeem my life.</i>

28:35.505 --> 28:37.052
<i>Justify it.</i>

28:37.216 --> 28:42.393
<i>Ah, look at the fierce one.
The fierceness in his eyes. The rage!</i>

28:42.554 --> 28:44.852
...inflicted upon myself...

28:46.725 --> 28:48.272
<i>Oh Billy.</i>

28:51.521 --> 28:53.068
<i>I died.</i>

28:55.067 --> 28:56.614
<i>In a different way.</i>

29:03.325 --> 29:05.748
<i>I know you don't love me.</i>

29:11.208 --> 29:12.926
<i>I know things.</i>

29:13.085 --> 29:16.089
<i>- Say it.
- Serious information.</i>

29:19.675 --> 29:21.348
<i>I've blinded you.</i>

29:23.762 --> 29:25.309
<i>My life has...</i>

29:25.472 --> 29:28.726
I did every lousy, crappy job
that they wanted me to do.

29:28.892 --> 29:33.068
<i>But because I stumbled down
the road like a drunk...</i>

29:36.191 --> 29:38.660
<i>that doesn't mean it's the wrong one.</i>

29:55.627 --> 29:58.096
<i>I turned you upside down.</i>

30:04.011 --> 30:05.558
<i>My son.</i>

30:13.729 --> 30:16.699
<i>The light's gone out of your eyes.</i>

30:19.693 --> 30:21.240
<i>Womanizer.</i>

30:26.825 --> 30:28.372
<i>Cut off.</i>

31:19.503 --> 31:21.505
<i>Life.</i>

31:27.052 --> 31:28.599
<i>A goddess.</i>

32:40.625 --> 32:42.172
Angela...

32:45.797 --> 32:47.344
Frita...

32:47.507 --> 32:52.138
<i>Music is very important.
Helps me to fall in love.</i>

32:52.888 --> 32:54.731
<i>I fall in love 20 times a day.</i>

32:54.890 --> 32:58.815
Your face was very familiar to me, but I
didn't know from where. You're fantastic.

32:58.977 --> 33:00.149
Thank you.

33:00.312 --> 33:05.534
Listening to music on headsets, unaware you
are staring at them like a dirty ol' man.

33:06.401 --> 33:08.699
<i>Myself, I didn't wanna get a divorce.</i>

33:08.862 --> 33:13.208
I never stopped loving them.
But the way I loved them changed.

33:14.242 --> 33:15.494
<i>They are like flavors.</i>

33:15.660 --> 33:20.712
<i>Sometimes you want raspberry, then
after a while you want some strawberry.</i>

33:20.874 --> 33:23.878
- It's Abrasive.
- Oh, you are such a governor.

33:31.092 --> 33:32.935
- What's your name?
- Helen.

33:35.222 --> 33:36.769
What's your name?

33:37.432 --> 33:38.479
Rick.

33:38.600 --> 33:40.318
Do you know anybody here?

33:40.685 --> 33:43.063
No. Does that surprise you?

33:51.446 --> 33:53.369
- I know a guy.
- I know a guy...

33:54.199 --> 33:58.579
- ...like future space.
- You're at a party, it's alright.

34:18.431 --> 34:20.809
You know who'd be hot?
Cleopatra.

34:20.976 --> 34:23.775
If her nose had been this much shorter,

34:23.937 --> 34:26.031
it would've changed the world.

34:47.168 --> 34:48.715
<i>The Pearl.</i>

34:52.716 --> 34:54.263
<i>Somewhere in the sea.</i>

35:00.348 --> 35:01.895
<i>A chaos.</i>

35:07.897 --> 35:09.444
<i>Hungry.</i>

35:11.484 --> 35:13.612
<i>Longing for something other...</i>

35:17.824 --> 35:19.667
<i>without knowing what it is.</i>

35:29.127 --> 35:31.926
What about pink?
Do you like pink?

35:33.465 --> 35:39.973
- I love the company of women.
- It's pretty. Did it take long?

35:40.138 --> 35:43.108
<i>It seemed they knew something.</i>

35:43.266 --> 35:45.189
Some men don't like pink.

35:45.352 --> 35:49.778
- <i>But closer.</i>
- Now you tell me something.

35:51.900 --> 35:53.743
<i>To the mystery.</i>

36:04.996 --> 36:07.624
<i>Treat this world as it deserves.</i>

36:10.043 --> 36:11.886
<i>There are no principles...</i>

36:13.296 --> 36:14.843
<i>just circumstances.</i>

36:22.222 --> 36:23.769
<i>Nobody's home.</i>

36:23.932 --> 36:27.436
<i>Smoke machines in an empty sea.</i>

36:27.602 --> 36:29.195
<i>I got women in Tennessee.</i>

36:29.354 --> 36:33.655
<i>What can run but never walk,
some word have I found but never talk.</i>

36:33.775 --> 36:35.869
<i>Gonna take me out to see...</i>

36:54.921 --> 36:56.468
<i>Get up.</i>

37:07.892 --> 37:09.610
<i>Find it.</i>

37:11.438 --> 37:16.410
<i>There's a ketamine party we're having
next week. Have you ever heard of that?</i>

37:16.526 --> 37:22.124
<i>You're here for 20 seconds and then,
wham, you're out. You're in another room.</i>

37:22.282 --> 37:25.832
Your wife. You're in another one.
You oughtta do that.

37:25.994 --> 37:29.715
Have you been to Sarajevo?
I have prayed, man,

37:29.873 --> 37:35.801
for God to take my arm, take both arms.
I felt so useless.

37:35.962 --> 37:37.714
What's your name?

38:13.374 --> 38:15.217
<i>Dear friend.</i>

38:17.629 --> 38:19.848
<i>I wonder where
I was in all that time.</i>

38:23.134 --> 38:24.681
<i>A sleepwalker.</i>

38:31.100 --> 38:33.819
<i>In love with the world,
in love with love.</i>

38:41.402 --> 38:43.951
<i>The world's a swamp.</i>

38:45.573 --> 38:47.246
<i>You have to fly over it.</i>

38:48.910 --> 38:50.628
<i>Fly...</i>

38:54.457 --> 38:56.004
<i>High up...</i>

38:58.962 --> 39:00.885
<i>where everything is just...</i>

39:02.173 --> 39:03.720
<i>a speck.</i>

39:29.117 --> 39:30.664
<i>You changed.</i>

39:36.749 --> 39:38.342
<i>The world absorbed you.</i>

39:44.507 --> 39:46.054
<i>More and more.</i>

39:55.310 --> 39:58.029
<i>I regret that it turned out the way it did.</i>

39:58.897 --> 40:01.946
<i>You always wanted to get away.
I wanted a mate.</i>

40:03.359 --> 40:04.906
<i>I couldn't have you.</i>

40:08.740 --> 40:10.583
<i>Just didn't wanna be alone.</i>

40:29.427 --> 40:31.976
Are you sorry that you brought me here?

40:37.185 --> 40:38.732
Are you sorry you came?

40:40.521 --> 40:45.197
Do you remember how happy we were?
Different these days.

40:47.695 --> 40:49.368
What's going on with you?

40:51.991 --> 40:56.497
You used to sing in the morning
coming down the stairs.

40:58.623 --> 41:01.752
I meant to make you happy.
I wanted nothing else.

41:03.044 --> 41:05.672
But then you began to be angry with me...

41:07.048 --> 41:08.641
just for little things.

41:12.178 --> 41:16.524
<i>I don't wanna accuse you,
but you turned more unkind toward me.</i>

41:19.894 --> 41:21.441
<i>Almost cruel.</i>

41:33.658 --> 41:36.537
Just don't threaten me with leaving, okay?

41:36.703 --> 41:38.376
Just do what you wanna do!

41:42.166 --> 41:43.759
Just go!

42:08.234 --> 42:10.407
<i>Stay.</i>

42:16.242 --> 42:17.789
<i>I want you.</i>

42:22.206 --> 42:23.753
<i>Hold you.</i>

42:25.960 --> 42:28.509
<i>Have you.
Mine.</i>

42:29.338 --> 42:32.342
<i>Are you sorry
we didn't have babies?</i>

42:36.804 --> 42:38.351
<i>I am.</i>

42:45.271 --> 42:47.194
<i>Got started so late.</i>

43:22.058 --> 43:27.030
<i>You wanted me to help you
through the dangers of a young man's life.</i>

43:27.855 --> 43:29.402
<i>Ambition.</i>

43:31.234 --> 43:32.781
<i>Fear.</i>

43:36.531 --> 43:39.660
When was the last time
you took these boots off?

43:46.833 --> 43:50.007
<i>I think you were afraid
of going astray.</i>

43:53.714 --> 43:56.513
<i>I couldn't help you stay on the right path.</i>

44:01.389 --> 44:04.359
<i>Your head was turned
in the wrong direction.</i>

44:05.226 --> 44:07.524
Can you move all your fingers?

44:08.896 --> 44:11.365
Yeah, they look a little bit bruised.

44:32.879 --> 44:37.350
<i>You never really wanted
to be totally inside our marriage.</i>

44:41.596 --> 44:43.189
<i>Nor outside it, either.</i>

44:50.438 --> 44:53.237
<i>You were sincere in the promises you made.</i>

44:59.864 --> 45:05.246
<i>Still... they didn't come from your heart.</i>

45:41.697 --> 45:44.075
<i>I was afraid when I was young.</i>

