01:24:18.345 --> 01:24:20.643
<i>I just teach this moment.</i>

01:24:22.558 --> 01:24:25.027
<i>Pay attention to this moment.</i>

01:24:27.729 --> 01:24:29.572
<i>And everything is there...</i>

01:24:32.234 --> 01:24:33.736
<i>perfect...</i>

01:24:36.238 --> 01:24:37.785
<i>and complete.</i>

01:24:40.867 --> 01:24:42.414
<i>Just as it is.</i>

01:25:10.355 --> 01:25:12.323
<i>You're so quiet.</i>

01:25:14.484 --> 01:25:16.703
<i>You keep everything to yourself.</i>

01:25:23.493 --> 01:25:25.040
<i>You have love in you.</i>

01:25:27.039 --> 01:25:28.586
<i>I know it.</i>

01:25:36.256 --> 01:25:37.803
<i>When I'm with you...</i>

01:25:39.134 --> 01:25:41.182
<i>I forget everything else.</i>

01:25:46.725 --> 01:25:48.693
<i>My husband...</i>

01:25:49.811 --> 01:25:51.358
<i>my life as I knew it.</i>

01:25:52.272 --> 01:25:58.575
Thumb, first finger, third
finger, left, fourth finger, third finger,

01:25:58.737 --> 01:26:05.837
<i>second finger, thumb, right hand, thumb,
first finger, second finger, thumb...</i>

01:26:08.121 --> 01:26:09.668
<i>Have I found you?</i>

01:26:22.969 --> 01:26:24.516
<i>Can it be?</i>

01:27:19.776 --> 01:27:21.323
<i>Answer me.</i>

01:27:32.164 --> 01:27:33.711
<i>So this is what we are.</i>

01:27:36.710 --> 01:27:38.257
<i>A fire.</i>

01:28:07.491 --> 01:28:09.038
<i>Come with me.</i>

01:28:19.044 --> 01:28:20.591
<i>Away.</i>

01:29:17.435 --> 01:29:18.982
Open your mouth.

01:29:41.293 --> 01:29:43.637
<i>I wanna go away with you.</i>

01:29:56.099 --> 01:29:57.646
<i>Marry you.</i>

01:30:43.063 --> 01:30:45.532
<i>Save what you can of your life.</i>

01:30:47.692 --> 01:30:49.239
<i>Look at me.</i>

01:30:53.365 --> 01:30:56.414
<i>Dan't lose it all
just because you've lost a part.</i>

01:31:53.383 --> 01:31:56.011
<i>I found out I was pregnant.</i>

01:32:01.057 --> 01:32:02.650
<i>Nate came back.</i>

01:32:10.650 --> 01:32:13.654
<i>And I wasn't sure if it was my husband's...</i>

01:32:18.658 --> 01:32:20.205
<i>or if it was yours.</i>

01:32:36.509 --> 01:32:39.183
<i>...to distract me right now</i>

01:32:39.345 --> 01:32:41.598
<i>but I wanted to tel! you, to...</i>

01:32:42.348 --> 01:32:45.443
acknowledge that it was...

01:32:49.355 --> 01:32:50.902
I wake up and...

01:32:52.817 --> 01:32:55.866
I forget about it
for a few minutes and then...

01:32:59.657 --> 01:33:01.534
and then I remember.

01:33:09.042 --> 01:33:14.139
She's like "I had four of them.
You have to get over it and stop crying."

01:33:45.954 --> 01:33:47.877
<i>What are we now?</i>

01:34:37.463 --> 01:34:39.010
<i>Forgive me.</i>

01:36:22.402 --> 01:36:26.452
<i>There's so much love inside us.</i>

01:36:31.744 --> 01:36:33.291
<i>That never gets out.</i>

01:36:58.813 --> 01:37:00.486
<i>Have mercy on me.</i>

01:37:03.401 --> 01:37:05.699
<i>According to your unfailing love,</i>

01:37:08.990 --> 01:37:11.209
<i>your great compassion,</i>

01:37:13.077 --> 01:37:15.830
<i>blot out my transgressions.</i>

01:37:39.562 --> 01:37:41.109
<i>My son.</i>

01:37:44.442 --> 01:37:45.989
<i>I know you.</i>

01:37:52.283 --> 01:37:54.206
<i>I know you have a soul.</i>

01:38:15.139 --> 01:38:17.483
<i>Seems you're alone.</i>

01:38:19.143 --> 01:38:20.690
<i>You're not.</i>

01:38:22.397 --> 01:38:26.652
<i>Even now,
He's taking your hand and guiding you</i>

01:38:26.818 --> 01:38:28.365
<i>by a way you cannot see.</i>

01:38:30.363 --> 01:38:34.664
If you are unhappy, you shouldn't
take it as a mark of God's disfavor.

01:38:36.327 --> 01:38:40.958
Just the contrary.
Might be the very sign He loves you.

01:38:41.124 --> 01:38:45.800
He shows His love
not by helping you avoid suffering,

01:38:45.962 --> 01:38:49.182
by sending you suffering,

01:38:51.968 --> 01:38:53.515
<i>by keeping you there.</i>

01:38:57.473 --> 01:39:01.068
To suffer binds you to something
higher than yourself,

01:39:01.227 --> 01:39:03.275
higher than your own will.

01:39:03.438 --> 01:39:05.281
Takes you from the world

01:39:06.107 --> 01:39:09.361
to find what lies beyond it.

01:39:13.698 --> 01:39:18.750
<i>We are not only to endure
patiently the troubles He sends,</i>

01:39:18.911 --> 01:39:20.913
<i>we are to regard them as gifts.</i>

01:39:25.042 --> 01:39:28.262
<i>As gifts more precious</i>

01:39:28.379 --> 01:39:31.223
<i>than the happiness we wish for ourselves.</i>

01:39:49.400 --> 01:39:51.323
<i>Just left you behind.</i>

01:39:55.948 --> 01:39:57.666
<i>To get burned up.</i>

01:41:09.146 --> 01:41:10.693
<i>How do I begin?</i>

01:42:02.241 --> 01:42:03.743
<i>Father.</i>

01:42:10.082 --> 01:42:11.629
<i>Give me courage.</i>

01:42:16.797 --> 01:42:18.344
<i>Strength.</i>

01:42:21.344 --> 01:42:23.096
<i>I'm proud of you.</i>

01:42:24.388 --> 01:42:25.935
<i>You've done well.</i>

01:42:29.810 --> 01:42:31.608
<i>Better than me.</i>

01:42:33.856 --> 01:42:36.234
<i>Which is the way it's supposed to be.</i>

01:44:29.263 --> 01:44:32.233
<i>Find the light
you know in the east.</i>

01:44:34.810 --> 01:44:36.483
<i>As a child.</i>

01:44:42.026 --> 01:44:43.573
<i>The moon.</i>

01:44:45.112 --> 01:44:46.659
<i>The stars.</i>

01:44:53.454 --> 01:44:55.377
<i>They serve you.</i>

01:44:58.375 --> 01:45:00.377
<i>They guide you on your way.</i>

01:45:07.718 --> 01:45:10.221
<i>The light in the eyes of others.</i>

01:45:17.019 --> 01:45:18.566
<i>The pearl.</i>

01:46:01.146 --> 01:46:02.693
Wake up.

01:46:23.043 --> 01:46:24.590
<i>Turn.</i>

01:46:34.346 --> 01:46:35.893
<i>Look.</i>

01:46:41.103 --> 01:46:42.650
<i>Come out.</i>

01:47:30.319 --> 01:47:31.866
<i>My son.</i>

01:47:41.497 --> 01:47:43.044
<i>Remember.</i>

01:50:32.751 --> 01:50:34.298
<i>Begin.</i>

